The best free learning app for kids, free learning app for toddlers, free learning app for preschool, and free learning app for kindergarten.Everyone loves tracing, kids can learn using the best free learning app on your mobile device.

reviews.title: LOUSY!
reviews.comment: My child cries everytime it stops and says to puchase. Not to mention the stupid ad that pops up. Uninstalling. Not worth it. Not child friendly. DO NOT INSTALL.
reviews.author: Teresa Pickering

reviews.title: Dont waste your time.
reviews.comment: The game said it was free then when I sat down with my son to the abc part or the game (the only part we tried) it only let him go to the letter c and then said you dont own this item go to the store and purchase the game. Uninstalling now.
reviews.author: Brandi Grebe

reviews.title: No
reviews.comment: Filled with adds yet still charges for full version. Not kid friendly, boring and dull.
reviews.author: Megan Chillemi

reviews.title: Don\'t bother

reviews.comment: This would be a goof app if, 1.there wasn\'t so many ads popping up. 2. If it did more than just ABC and 123. You have to buy more letters ..
